N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4226.2 - Failure of horse to start

State Regulations

If a horse whose number has been exhibited or whose
starting is obligatory does not start and run in the race, the steward or
judges may suspend any person or persons responsible
therefor. Notes
